description: At Makers & Tasters (the lively market located right in the heart of Honolulu), you’ll find this Shaka Shrimp truck shaking things up with their shockingly delicious shrimp dishes.Their succulent selection includes Garlic Shrimp, Lemon Butter Shrimp, and Steak & Shrimp, and it all tastes simply of savory perfection.For some supreme island eating, ship yourself on out to Shaka Shrimp!
name: Shaka Shrimp
